#: ../../../policy/CMP0215.rst:2
msgid "CMP0215"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../policy/CMP0215.rst:6
msgid ":ref:`Ninja Generators` emit Swift modules separately from compilation."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../policy/CMP0215.rst:8
msgid ""
"In CMake 4.3 and below, Swift targets built by :ref:`Ninja Generators` emit "
"``.swiftmodule`` from the Swift compile edge together with object files. "
"Because Ninja treats a build edge as atomic, downstream Swift targets must "
"wait for compilation outputs to finish before they can use the module "
"interface."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../policy/CMP0215.rst:14
msgid ""
"CMake 4.4 and above prefer to emit ``.swiftmodule`` from a dedicated ``-emit-"
"module`` build edge so that downstream Swift targets can begin compiling as "
"soon as the module interface is available.  This policy provides "
"compatibility with projects that have not been updated."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../policy/CMP0215.rst:19
msgid ""
"The ``OLD`` behavior for this policy is to not emit modules separately. The "
"``NEW`` behavior for this policy is to emit ``.swiftmodule`` from a "
"dedicated build edge for importable Swift targets by default."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../policy/CMP0215.rst:23
msgid ""
"The :prop_tgt:`Swift_SEPARATE_MODULE_EMISSION` target property and "
"corresponding :variable:`CMAKE_Swift_SEPARATE_MODULE_EMISSION` variable may "
"be set to enable or disable the behavior on a per-target basis."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../policy/CMP0215.rst:29
msgid ""
"Separate module emission takes effect only when policy :policy:`CMP0157` is "
"set to ``NEW`` prior to the first :command:`project` or :command:"
"`enable_language` command that enables the Swift language. The dedicated ``."
"swiftmodule`` edge is available only in the split Swift build model."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../policy/include/STANDARD_ADVICE.rst:1
msgid ""
"This policy was introduced in CMake version |INTRODUCED_IN_CMAKE_VERSION|. "
"It may be set by :command:`cmake_policy` or :command:"
"`cmake_minimum_required`. If it is not set, CMake |WARNS_OR_DOES_NOT_WARN|, "
"and uses ``OLD`` behavior."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../policy/include/DEPRECATED.rst:2
msgid ""
"The ``OLD`` behavior of a policy is :ref:`deprecated by definition <cmake-"
"policies-intro>` and may be removed in a future version of CMake."
msgstr ""
